PN,41101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,FFive members of a gang supplying
OL,8,Faround half a million pounds worth of
OL,9,Fdrugs from addresses in Bournemouth,
OL,10,FChristchurch and Southampton have been
OL,11,Fjailed for a total of 59 years.
OL,13,FThe group supplied 27.5 kilos of
OL,14,Fcocaine to areas across the UK
OL,15,Fincluding London, West Sussex,
OL,16,FCumbria, Avon and Somerset, Dorset,
OL,17,FDevon, Cornwall and Hampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,FThe men, who are originally from
OL,8,FAlbania, were arrested after an
OL,9,Finvestigation by the South West
OL,10,FRegional Organised Crime Squad.
OL,12,FAt one of the properties in
OL,13,FBournemouth, police body cam footage
OL,14,Frevealed some of the cocaine that was
OL,15,Fbeing prepared for distribution.
OL,17,FXhetan Gjoci, 31, of Waterloo Road,
OL,18,FBournemouth, Vladimir Rina, 37, of
OL,19,FRichmond Road, Bournemouth, and Dejvin
OL,20,FRina of Soberton Road, Bournemouth
OL,21,Fwere the ringleaders.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,FThey were supported in their operation
OL,8,Fby Korab Skepi, 23, of Bellevue Road,
OL,9,FSouthampton and Arlend Titini, 32, of
OL,10,FTurnstone Gardens in Southampton.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the group were
OL,13,Fconvicted DC Danielle Hill of SWROCU
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was a protracted and
OL,15,Fcomplex investigation which was
OL,16,Fsupported by colleagues in Dorset
OL,17,FPolice, Hampshire Police, the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police and Cumbria Police.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,F"We have worked tirelessly to build a
OL,8,Frobust case against this OCG who were
OL,9,Fhandling substantial volumes of cash
OL,10,Fand preparing vast amounts of cocaine
OL,11,Fworth hundreds of thousands of pounds
OL,12,Fand delivering it to a network of
OL,13,Fbuyers using sophisticated 'hides'
OL,14,Fwithin their vehicles.
OL,16,F"We welcome the sentences passed by
OL,17,Fthe judge and remain committed to
OL,18,Ftargeting criminals involved in
OL,19,Fserious and organised crime in the
OL,20,FSouth West and beyond."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,FJames Foster, Specialist Prosecutor at
OL,8,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service said:
OL,9,F"This organised crime group was part
OL,10,Fof a sophisticated plot to flood our
OL,11,Fstreets with cocaine.
OL,13,F"The defendants went to significant
OL,14,Flengths to organise and conceal their
OL,15,Fcriminal activity, including using
OL,16,FrentedJaccommodation to prepare drugs
OL,17,Ffor supply and sourcing specialist
OL,18,Fequipment online.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,F"Working closely with the South West
OL,8,FRegional Organised Crime Unit, the CPS
OL,9,Fwas able to present compelling
OL,10,Fevidence of a largescale operation,
OL,11,Fresulting in guilty pleas from all.
OL,13,F"More than 27 kilos of cocaine along
OL,14,Fwith over #167,000 in cash were seized
OL,15,Fpreventing a substantial quantity of
OL,16,Fharmful drugs from reaching our
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,F"Their attempts to disguise their
OL,8,Factivities did not prevent them from
OL,9,Fbeing caught, and the substantial
OL,10,Fprison sentences passed today reflect
OL,11,Fthe seriousness of this offending and
OL,12,Fthe scale of the criminal enterprise
OL,13,Finvolved."
OL,15,FDetective Superintendent Emma
OL,16,FSweetzer, Dorset Police's Director of
OL,17,FIntelligence, said: "We know the
OL,18,Fimpact that drug-related activity has
OL,19,Fon communities and we remain
OL,20,Fabsolutely committed to doing all we
OL,21,Fcan to prevent it from occurring.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]yD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776700609
OL,3,CGang who prepared half a million
OL,4,Cpounds worth of cocaine in makeshift
OL,5,Clab jailed
OL,7,F"Working closely with partners and
OL,8,Fpolicing colleagues, we were able to
OL,9,Fdisrupt the activity of an OCG
OL,10,Fsupplying cocaine in Dorset and across
OL,11,Fthe country and ensure five men faced
OL,12,Fjustice for their involvement.
OL,14,F"I want to thank everyone involved for
OL,15,Ftheir work in taking these illegal and
OL,16,Fdangerous substances off the streets
OL,17,Fand protecting Dorset's communities
OL,18,Ffrom the harm they can cause."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@^O]
